Java Assignment - Student Grade Management System 
Objective 
Write a Java program to manage students' grades using the concepts learned so far. 
Program Requirements 
Assume there are 5 students and each student has grades in 3 subjects. 
Step 1 
Ask user to enter the names of the 5 students and their grades 
Step 2 - Main Menu 
Display the below menu: 
1. Show All Students names. 
2. Show all Students grades in each subject.  
3. Search Student by name. 
4. Count Passed Students 
0. Exit 
Input Validation 
Grades must be between 0 and 100. If an invalid grade is entered, print 'Invalid grade.' and 
ask again. 
Bonus 
• Display average for each subject. 
• Display highest grade in each subject. 
• Display letter grades (A-F). 
• Grade >= 85 → A. 
• Grade >= 75 → B. 
• Grade >= 65 → C. 
• Grade >= 50 → D. 
• Otherwise → F. 
